goal: an app connected to an ai that lets you specify the topic which you want to study.
      the app will then use ai to make quizlet like study-environment for your personalized needs.

techstack: index.php
           jquery
           deepseek-r1:7b

mvp: php app with different inputs and labels. data is sent to ai (ollama)
     ollamafile to process inputs accordingly and send back data to api to display.


prototype:


REQUEST from CLIENT
curl http://localhost:11434/api/generate -d '{
  "model": "phi3.5",
  "prompt": "Why is the sky blue?",
  "stream": false
}'


